---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import ProjectPageShell from "../components/ProjectPageShell.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
    title="Modern Football - REDriver Works"
    description="Modern Football is REDriver Works' tactical football project: reactive, simulation-first, and built without stale genre baggage."
    bodyClass="project-page"
>
    <ProjectPageShell
        themeClass="project-theme-football"
        eyebrow="Sports Weirdness"
        title="Modern Football"
        intro="A football project built from scratch with no loyalty to stale sports-game habits. Tactical, reactive, and trying very hard not to insult the sport."
        status="Core systems are still being pushed around. The simulation is getting smarter, and the project keeps getting more ambitious instead of calming down."
        sideNote="The goal is not just to look like football. The goal is to feel like football decisions actually matter from moment to moment."
        stats={[
            { value: "AI", label: "Under pressure" },
            { value: "Tactics", label: "Core language" },
            { value: "WIP", label: "No fake launch date" },
        ]}
        panels={[
            {
                kicker: "Vision",
                title: "Start fresh and stop inheriting bad sports-game habits.",
                body: [
                    "Most football games are polished iterations of old assumptions. Modern Football starts by questioning those assumptions instead of treating them like sacred genre law.",
                    "That means smarter simulation, cleaner tactical feedback, and gameplay that reacts like a sport with ideas in it, not just a bag of canned animations."
                ]
            },
            {
                kicker: "Philosophy",
                title: "Built different, yes, but for actual reasons.",
                body: [
                    "What if the AI understood shape, pressure, risk, and timing better? What if player behavior felt less like a script and more like a system under tension?",
                    "Those are the questions this project keeps circling. If the answer is just another yearly football machine, then the whole exercise was pointless."
                ]
            },
            {
                kicker: "Status",
                title: "Still in the lab, because half-baked sports systems are miserable.",
                body: [
                    "The work right now is deep in the ugly middle: systems work, experimentation, and constant reshaping whenever the simulation reveals a better idea.",
                    "When something is worth showing, it will land here first. Until then, the project gets the time it needs."
                ]
            }
        ]}
        links={[
            { href: "/", label: "Back to Homepage", variant: "secondary" },
            { href: "/modern-football/#top", label: "Stay on Signal" },
        ]}
    />
</BaseLayout>
